More details ﻿ BEERS ON TAP FOOD TRUCKS & EVENTS SPECIAL UPCOMING EVENTS: 8/28 - GRASS LEAGUE COLLAB BEER RELEASE NIGHT 9/27 - GOLFTOBER FEST Pairing up our two favorite pastimes THE BEER & GOLF CONNECTION At the core of it all, we’re passionate craft beer lovers who met through the game of golf. Dogleg Brewing Company celebrates the game that brought us together through exceptional craft beer served up with a fun, engaging tasting room experience. We can’t wait for you to join the fun! Steeped in tradition. beer st yles for every taste Driven by passion. Steeped in tradition. We brew beer with passion and precision in the pursuit of excellence. Dogleg celebrates the game that united us and the craft that ignited our creative brewing spirit. We offer a diverse and wonderful range of beer styles that cater to a variety of tastes and preferences. From the hoppy and tropical notes of our Dogleg Pale to the roast malt flavors of our Origins Scotch Ale, there is something for everyone to enjoy at Dogleg Brewing Co. BEERS ON TAP Calling craft beer enthusiasts and golf fanatics alike! join the DOGLEG BEER CLUB! Members get access to R&D beer tastings, special events, outings & more. JOIN THE CLUB create your own memorable experience HOST YOUR EVENT AT DOGLEG Whether you’re celebrating a milestone event, planning a holiday party for your staff, hosting a corporate hoppy hour or looking to wow your clients, Dogleg Brewing Company offers a wide variety of private events packages both large and small.
